data.description: This is a rare opportunity to be the proud owner of an incredible historic 1905 Victorian home full of original wooden molding , flooring and grand pocket doors.  With almost 3000 sq ft of finished living space including a parlor, family room with wood burning fireplace,  dinning room and eat in kitchen holiday entertaining will be amazing.  Access the second floor from the private kitchen steps or the main staircase. Upstairs you will find 4 large bedrooms and a full bath.  This grand home also has a walk up third floor that could be guest rooms, office space, an artist studio or finished bonus spaces of your liking.  The full walk out basement houses 200 amp electric service, updated heating and plumbing and is currently being used as a work shop. Outside at the rear of the home there is both a lower and upper porch with an oversized 1 car, drive through garage with tons of storage space and high ceilings.  Schedule a tour today.
